title: Ep. 506 - Police Reach On Time - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Kutkutiya comes and gets hold of the children. He threatens to harm them. The police reach just on time and Gokuldham society rejoices with relief.

title: Ep. 507 - Jetha Gets A New Helper - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha envies the crow who gets to eat what he does not. When he goes to the office, he sees someone at the shop and enquires who is he. He turns out to be Nattu's nephew.

title: Ep. 508 - Lacchuram's Helplessness - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Lacchuram visits Jetha's office and gives him paint worth 2 Lack rupees. When enquired, Lacchram tells him that he is helpless and has no other option to pay his debts.

title: Ep. 509 - Sodhi's Intelligence - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha now has a task to sell all the paint bottles that he has. He tries talking to Bhide about it but he has already left the house. Seeing Sodhi, he tries convincing 'the most intelligent' person to paint his house.

title: Ep. 510 - The Confusion Of Identity - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha goes to his office panting and tells Gada to increase the AC to full. Jetha sends off Gada to the godown. Meanwhile, some customers come and Jetha has a confusion of identity.

title: Ep. 511 - No New Year Party In Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu Sena decides to ask Bhide regarding the new year celebrations at Gokuldham society. However, when Tapu asks Bhide, he tells there will be no new year celebrations this year.

title: Ep. 512 - Taarak's Plan - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak decides that they have to celebrate the new year's eve. All the men decide to go without telling their wives. However, none of them are good at lying.

title: Ep. 513 - Babuji Punishes The Men - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone catches the men redhanded when they are about to start their 'party'. Babuji gets angry and punishes all the men involved in it.

title: Ep. 514 - Bhide's Notice - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide talks with a contractor for the painting of their society. After all the formalities with the contractor are done, Bhide writes a notice on the board.

title: Ep. 515 - A Tiff Between Bhide And Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The contractor fills all the cracks and tells Bhide that he will need more money to buy the paints. Jetha plays his game and tells Bhide that he has color and that they should use it. Bhide calls Jetha selfish and both have an argument.

title: Ep. 516 - Sakharam Leaves The Job Undone - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sakharam is told that he will have to work with the paint provided by Jetha. This angers Sakharam and he leaves the job undone. He also informs all the other contractors to not take Gokuldham society's contract.

title: Ep. 517 - Babuji Steps In - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After Sakharam refuses to work, everyone puts the blame on Jetha and Bhide asks Jetha to go and get workers to start painting again. Babuji tells Jetha that it is not his mistake and starts painting the society himself.

title: Ep. 518 - Strength In Unity - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sakharam visits the Gokuldham society and does not believe his eyes after he sees that the society painted. When he asks who did it, Babuji replies that there is strength in unity.

title: Ep. 519 - Nattu Kaka Is Back - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gada makes a blunder and spoils the relation between Jetha and an old client. Jetha sees Gada as a huge disturbance and a threat to the business. Nattu Kaka comes back and there is no one more relieved than Jetha.

title: Ep. 520 - The Satyanarayan Puja - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After the painting of the society is over, Babuji decides to have a Satyanarayan Puja in society. Madhavi and Bhide are told to sit for the Puja and then Babuji have a surprise for everyone.
